  "3275440": {
    "name": "Pluralys",
    "steam_appid": 3275440,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你操控的Elie今年16岁。一个普通的少年（少女？），好奇心旺盛，有点爱做梦，还是个游戏迷。他（她…？）最喜欢和好朋友Gab和Medie一起扮演角色，虚构自己的世界。Elie跟妈妈和妹妹住在G区——妹妹有时很难带（不过这种年龄嘛，可以理解）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elie的世界看上去平常无奇：人们上班、处理日常烦心事……总之，一切都很正常（嗯，除了Zeings这些怪东西，不过那个当另说）。直到有一天，有人在Messenger Plus!上联系你。一个神秘的人突然对你说出那句潜在英雄都会听到的话：“只有你能改变这一切。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但为什么偏偏是你？你又是否愿意相信这个陌生人？这款游戏来自一个全加拿大的热血开发团队。两年倾力打造，没有任何AI介入，所有内容均为原创，由一群热爱RPG的游戏人用心完成:-) 我们由衷希望，你能喜欢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/a54b823c3dea9a1e8ec385cea7a75c74.poster.avif?t=1769811954\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/a54b823c3dea9a1e8ec385cea7a75c74.webm?t=1769811954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/a54b823c3dea9a1e8ec385cea7a75c74.mp4?t=1769811954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pluralys的世界既熟悉，又充满诡秘。那里生活着来自别处的生命，他们就隐藏在芸芸众生之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们究竟是什么？他们打算永远留在你的星球吗？他们能成为你的朋友吗？他们所有都？也许答案全取决于你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/99572c37d85b0e669b072cb6ac5ed081.poster.avif?t=1769811954\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/99572c37d85b0e669b072cb6ac5ed081.webm?t=1769811954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/99572c37d85b0e669b072cb6ac5ed081.mp4?t=1769811954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >联系你的那个神秘人，交给你一件奇怪的装置：Pager。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个特殊的工具能够冻结时间，显示出别人看不到的细节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有了它，你可以分析人物、移动常人无法搬动的重物、破解安保系统，甚至做更多事……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/e8763a7ea5ca1db13e7863cbc68cc3ce.poster.avif?t=1769811954\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/e8763a7ea5ca1db13e7863cbc68cc3ce.webm?t=1769811954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/e8763a7ea5ca1db13e7863cbc68cc3ce.mp4?t=1769811954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然了，不是每个场景都需要靠pager（90年代的人可能不这么想）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pluralys是一个有生命的世界，充满大大小小的挑战，还有散落在旅途中的各种小游戏：谨慎选择、解开谜题、面对难题……游戏中有大量互动，让你用新奇的方式探索这个世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/20668920993cfaf4620aeee6fee70e04.poster.avif?t=1769811954\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/20668920993cfaf4620aeee6fee70e04.webm?t=1769811954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/20668920993cfaf4620aeee6fee70e04.mp4?t=1769811954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的旅程有时悠闲惬意，有时充满阻碍，但无论怎样，你都会走进丰富多彩、意想不到的环境：宁静的住宅区、热闹的集市、辽阔的沙漠、神秘的实验室……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个地点都有自己的故事，而每一次探索，都会让你离真相更近一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/3c86453943f66e16157ce77fb6b2b181.poster.avif?t=1769811954\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/3c86453943f66e16157ce77fb6b2b181.webm?t=1769811954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275440/extras/3c86453943f66e16157ce77fb6b2b181.mp4?t=1769811954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情，是Pluralys的核心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中，你会看到许多短小的过场动画——有时温馨、有时搞笑、有时带着神秘色彩。它们让角色关系更立体，也一步步揭开这个世界背后的秘密。游戏中没有战斗，只有真正重要的决策时刻。</p>",
